title: H2 Pub Capture
body:
This is a final project that was done to find happy hours in the Belltown area of Seattle. What me and my team of 4 wanted to be able to not miss a happy hour again. It/'s written in vanilla javascript with a table listing the bars in Belltown with a ticker countdown until the happy hour ends.
